      <p>[Identification of item,] [date (if known)]; Arthur Robert Smith Collection, Coll. 36,
        box_, folder_, The Edgar Cayce Foundation, Virginia Beach, Virginia.</p>
    </prefercite>
    <scopecontent id="aspace_1e046189b35a09d318c4316122ed8d44">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>This collection includes correspondence, interview transcripts, notes, and research sources
        collected by Arthur Robert Smith to write the book entitled About My Father's Business
        (1988), a biography of Hugh Lynn Cayce (1907-1982).</p>
    </scopecontent>
